title: Bronze IV looking for semi serious ranked team
body:
Played a lot in S1/2 but haven't played much at all since then up until recently, was gold back in the day.
Keen to start doing some ranked team, have never been in a ranked team before.

Love to play leo, nami, sona 

OCE: Dunkdownduckdown

Add me in game if you want to chat!

replies.body:
Love to play with ya man !
